		<mj-raw><!-- Hero: background image, centered headline + CTA --></mj-raw>
		<mj-section css-class="hero-4" background-url="https://prod.cdn.everyaction.com/images/van/EWG/EWG/1/71381/images/emailify/5875a0c66fa6021a789bfa45c2559390.jpg" padding="16px 0px 380px 0px" text-align="center">
			<mj-column vertical-align="top" width="100%" padding="24px">
				<mj-text mj-class="h3 centered" css-class="text-h3" font-size="30px" padding-bottom="24px">
					<p>Trump administration backs Bayer in Supreme Court fight, putting corporate interests over Roundup victims</p>
				</mj-text>
				<mj-button background-color="#203a3b" href="https://act.ewg.org/nrfMs7W5QU6qMaHkaV4lMg2?sourceid=1023696&utm_source=newsletter&utm_campaign=202602FebNews7&utm_medium=email&utm_content=default&nvep=&hmac=&emci=c973bf0e-bd0d-f111-a69a-000d3a57593f&emdi=ea000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000001&ceid=" width="154px">Read More</mj-button>
			</mj-column>
		</mj-section>

		<mj-raw><!-- Anniversary section --></mj-raw>
		<mj-section background-url="https://prod.cdn.everyaction.com/images/van/EWG/EWG/1/71381/images/emailify/e3fe1bff9a3f0985d65823a17dd40c35.jpg" padding="32px">
			<mj-column width="576px">
				<mj-text mj-class="h3 white" css-class="text-h3" align="left" padding-bottom="16px">
					<p>EWG'S 30TH ANNIVERSARY</p>
				</mj-text>
				<mj-text mj-class="body white" css-class="text-body" align="left" padding-bottom="16px">
					<p>EWG is celebrating 30 years of helping you to protect your health and environment. Individuals like you account for more than half of EWG's revenue and are essential to our success. <a href="https://act.ewg.org/O6Wq1SkLXEam4cmOkmwkyA2?sourceid=1022286&utm_source=newsletter&utm_campaign=202401Newsletter8&utm_medium=email&utm_content=default&nvep=&hmac=&emci=e14c20b5-bd0d-f111-a69a-000d3a57593f&emdi=ea000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000001&ceid=" class="link-green" target="_blank">Help us celebrate this anniversary and fund the work you count on with a donation today.</a></p>
				</mj-text>
				<mj-text mj-class="body green" css-class="text-body" align="left" font-weight="700" padding-bottom="16px">
					<p>CAN WE COUNT ON YOU TO JOIN OUR COMMUNITY OF OVER 400,000 SUPPORTERS TODAY?</p>
				</mj-text>
